      <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(3rem,8vw,6rem)] tracking-wider text-[#e8e8e8] leading-none">
        SHIP<br/><span class="text-acid acid-glow">BETTER SVG</span><span class="opacity-30"> TODAY.</span>
